.DT
recover
Discworld player help
recover

.SH Name
.SI 5
recover - allows to you recover recently buried items.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
recover [items]
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command will allow you to recover an item that was recently buried.
It will only work for recently buried items, so do not wait too long
before attempting to recover the items.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> bury corpse
You tidy up the place, clearing away a corpse of a bodyguard.
> recover corpse
You recover the corpse from the area.
.EI

.SH See Also
.SP 5 5
bury
.EP
